The laughter ride starts with Kapil speaking about the difference of the parties being held by the high class people and lower class people, the one liners and jokes has everyone in splits. Kapil then asks the audience to put forward their opinion about the parties. Later, a few kids come on the stage and trouble Kapil. The kid's skating coach joins them on the stage and Raju recognizes the team from the forthcoming movie, Hawa Hawai. After sometime, Dadi, who is dressed as a Spider Woman followed by Vivek Oberoi joins Kapil on the stage. A laugh riot follows with the participation of Raju, Dadi, the audience and top of all, Vivek Oberoi. After Vivek leaves, Kapil prepares for the challenge ahead. watch and have fun.
